0on%20the%20side%20of%20caution%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20some%20instances%20of%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffreelancer-use-ai-double-output-client-fired-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20fired%20for%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224db65718-4ef1-472b-8529-889d482691ce%5C%22%3EThe%20majority%20of%20workers%20aren't%20receiving%20that%20much%20AI%20training%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20execs%20rush%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20into%20their%20companies%2C%20workers%20might%20not%20be%20adequately%20equipped%20to%20keep%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20found%20that%2061%25%20of%20workers%20have%20spent%20less%20than%20five%20hours%20learning%20how%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20while%2030%25%20said%20they%20haven't%20had%20any%20AI%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20become%20a%20major%20oversight%20as%20AI%20continues%20to%20affect%20jobs.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fpublications%2Fthe-future-of-jobs-report-2023%2Fdigest%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAll%2520but%2520two%2520technologies%2520are%2Cin%2520the%2520next%2520five%2520years.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20estimated%20that%2044%25%20of%20workers'%20skills%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bdisrupted%26quot%3B%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Slack%20study%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Blearning%20and%20skill%20building%26quot%3B%20ranked%20first%20on%20lists%20of%20activities%20that%20executives%20wanted%20workers%20to%20prioritize%20and%20lists%20of%20what%20workers%20wished%20AI%20gave%20them%20more%20time%20to%20concentrate%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4336ce0-e9f0-4407-8c9e-bbdcbec526e4%5C%22%3EWorkers%20are%20concerned%20that%20the%20time%20they%20save%20with%20AI%20will%20increase%20their%20workload%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENinety-seven%20percent%20of%20executives%20surveyed%20say%20they%20feel%20%26quot%3Bsome%20level%20of%20urgency%26quot%3B%20to%20mix%20AI%20into%20their%20business%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20though%20AI%20has%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-saving-sales-teams-hours-work-daily-survey-says-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20professionals%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20more%20menial%20activities%2C%20like%20writing%20messages%2C%20workers%20in%20the%20survey%20said%20the%20extra%20free%20time%20may%20be%20filled%20with%20even%20more%20tasks%20and%20result%20in%20a%20higher%20workload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20which%20common%20work%20task%20AI%20is%20best%20at%20assisting%2C%20administration%20was%20the%20top%20answer.%20But%20when%20asked%20what%20workers%20would%20do%20with%20the%20potential%20time%20saved%20by%20AI%2C%20respondents%20said%20they%20would%20spend%20those%20hours%20on%20even%20more%20administrative%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c3e415a-9d4c-488f-af3c-fe2ccee9c262%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20AI%20users%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20turn%20to%20AI%20than%20colleagues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20survey%2C%2081%25%20of%20AI%20users%20said%20they%20ask%20AI%20for%20assistance%20or%20advice%20rather%20than%20a%20friend%20or%20peer.%20The%20main%20drivers%20of%20the%20trend%20were%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%2C%20with%2030%25%20and%2033%25%20respectively%20frequently%20consulting%20AI%20in%20place%20of%20a%20colleague.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESlack's%20survey%20included%2017%2C372%20workers%20in%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Canada%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20India%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Spain%2C%20Sweden%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20It%20was%20fielded%20between%20August%202-August%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslack-survey-desk-workers-interesting-