Nominating%20Rubio%20is%20especially%20notable%20for%20the%20Florida%20senator's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSenMarcoRubio%2Fstatus%2F1855002858262766019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethorny%20relationship%20with%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20steadfast%20support%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20what%20US-Chinese%20relations%20will%20look%20like%20if%20he's%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20Trump%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20they%20were%20confident%20Rubio%20would%20be%20the%20president-elect's%20nomination.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20Trump%20confirmed%20the%20pick%2C%20calling%20Rubio%20%26quot%3Ba%20highly%20respected%20leader%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20our%20nation%2C%20a%20true%20friend%20to%20our%20allies%2C%20and%20a%20fearless%20warrior%20who%20will%20never%20back%20down%20to%20our%20adversaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Frubio-statement-on-nomination-to-lead-state-department%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERubio%20said%20he%20was%C2%A0%26quot%3Bhonored%26quot%3B%20to%20receive%20the%20nomination%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20President%20Trump%2C%20we%20will%20deliver%20peace%20through%20strength%20and%20always%20put%20the%20interests%20of%20Americans%20and%20America%20above%20all%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senator%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20out%20to%20for%20comment%2C%20Rubio's%20Senate%20office%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20his%20statement%20on%20the%20nomination.%20The%20Trump%20transition%20team%20and%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20in%20Washington%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22marco%20rubio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F580769c2c524021c008b558e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERubio%20and%20Trump%2C%20once%20rivals%2C%20appear%20aligned%20on%20issues%20related%20to%20China%20and%20Taiwan.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FJohn%20Raoux%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20winning%20his%20senate%20seat%20in%202010%2C%20Rubio%20has%20been%20an%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20China.%20He's%20repeatedly%20spoken%20out%20about%20China's%20ambitious%20military%20and%20political%20goals%2C%20economic%20power%2C%20and%20the%20US'%20response%20to%20its%20growing%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Beijing%20has%20taken%20note.%20In%202020%2C%20Rubio%20and%20other%20US%20Senators%20were%20sanctioned%20by%20Beijing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-53722811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERubio%20was%20sanctioned%2C%20or%20blacklisted%2C%20twice%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20first%20in%20retaliation%20for%20US%20measures%20against%20senior%20Chinese%20officials%20over%20the%20mass%20detainment%20and%20abuse%20of%20the%20Uyghur%20ethnic%20group%2C%20and%20the%20second%20after%20Rubio%20supported%20US%20sanctions%20against%20Chinese%20officials%20for%20their%20response%20to%20protests%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20Rubio%20has%20accused%20China%20of%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgrotesque%20campaign%20of%20genocide%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Uyghurs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20is%20whether%20China%20will%20lift%20the%20sanctions%20on%20Rubio%2C%20which%20may%20prohibit%20him%20from%20traveling%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20how%20Washington's%20relations%20with%20Beijing%20could%20be%20impacted%20if%20Rubio's%20confirmed.%20But%20China's%20actions%20haven't%20stopped%20Rubio%20from%20continuing%20to%20speak%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%202022%20talk%20with%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20Rubio%20said%20members%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20had%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20%26quot%3Bhid%20their%20true%20ambition%20to%20remake%20the%20global%20order%20and%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20nation.%20But%20they%20don't%20hide%20it%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20and%20top%20China%20watchers%20have%20indicated%20that%20China's%20goals%2C%20along%20with%20those%20of%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20North%20Korea%2C%20are%20to%20upend%20the%20US-led%20liberal%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20talk%2C%20Rubio%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20gravest%20threat%20facing%20America%20today%2C%20the%20challenge%20that%20will%20define%20this%20century%20and%20every%20generation%20represented%20here%2C%20is%20not%20climate%20change%2C%20the%20pandemic%2C%20or%20the%20left's%20version%20of%20social%20justice.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Ficymi-rubio-speaks-on-the-threat-of-communist-china-at-the-heritage-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20threat%20that%20will%20define%20this%20century%20is%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20Marco%20Rubio%20campaign%20in%20Florida%20ahead%20of%20the%202022%20midterms%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660acf1f16bde8d4ead40552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERubio's%20nomination%20raises%20questions%20about%20US%20relations%20with%20China%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20expressed%20similar%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20past%20and%20since%20then%2C%20criticizing%20what%20he%20has%20said%20is%20growing%20and%20ongoing%20Chinese%20economic%20and%20political%20influence%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThey%20have%20leverage%20over%20our%20economy.%20They%20have%20influence%20over%20our%20society.%20They%20have%20an%20army%20of%20unpaid%20lobbyists%20here%20in