nalytics%20and%20monetization%20and%20is%20offering%20features%20like%20podcast%20clips%2C%20where%20creators%20can%20promote%20episodes%20by%20uploading%20vertical%20short-form%20video%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotify's%20stock%20has%20been%20riding%20high%20this%20week%20after%20it%20reported%20Q3%20earnings.%20The%20company%20showed%20increased%20profitability%20(as%20measured%20by%20gross%20margin)%20and%20added%206%20million%20net%20paying%20subscribers%2C%20bringing%20its%20total%20to%20252%20million%20paying%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-battles-youtube-with-new-creator-video-revenue-sharing-program-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731536267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67352062ede4eeae392753a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-battles-youtube-with-new-creator-video-revenue-sharing-program-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spotify%20goes%20after%20YouTube's%20video%20podcast%20dominance%20by%20removing%20ads%20for%20paid%20subscribers%20and%20introducing%20a%20new%20revenue%20program%20for%20creators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aperelli%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Perelli%2CDan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-battles-youtube-with-new-creator-video-revenue-sharing-program-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sydney%20Sweeney%3A%20Hollywood%20Says%20It%E2%80%99s%20About%20%E2%80%98Women%20Empowering%20Other%20Women%E2%80%99%20but%20%E2%80%98All%20of%20It%20Is%20Fake%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98None%20of%20It%E2%80%99s%20Happening%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731536038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FGettyImages-2170739729