versimplify%20something%20that%20can%20be%20complicated.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20gamify%20the%20act%20of%20slashing%20government%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20and%20experts%20said%20it's%20a%20savvy%20strategy%20to%20get%20people%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20a%20dry%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20CEO%20said%20this%20week%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-leaderboard-federal-government-spending-trump-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20a%20public%20%26quot%3Bleaderboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20most%20insanely%20dumb%20spending%20of%20your%20tax%20dollars.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20both%20extremely%20tragic%20and%20extremely%20entertaining%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20posted%2C%20along%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20let%20the%20public%20weigh%20in%20on%20specific%20potential%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20would%20create%20the%20leaderboard%20as%20part%20of%20a%20new%20position%20in%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%3A%20head%20of%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-doge-government-efficiency-what-us-spends-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%2C%20which%20would%20be%20charged%20with%20cutting%20federal%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20all%20the%20activities%20of%20DOGE%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20will%20lead%20alongside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-department-government-efficiency-doge-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusinessman%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20which%20is%20named%20after%20a%20Musk-linked%20cryptocurrency%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20published%20online%20in%20the%20name%20of%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20Musk's%20leaderboard%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20revealed%20his%20marketing%20savvy%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20could%20also%20encourage%20%26quot%3Bgotcha%26quot%3B%20moments%20that%20need%20more%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20promises%20entertainment%2C%20competition%2C%20and%20interactivity%20marketed%20to%20a%20group%20with%20skin%20in%20the%20game%3A%20the%20American%20public%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20their%20tax%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20would%20turn%20an%20often%20wonky%20exercise%20%E2%80%94%20government%20budgeting%20%E2%80%94%20into%20a%20participatory%20game%20of%20winners%20and%20losers.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20it%20would%20also%20likely%20give%20Musk%20a%20valuable%20prize%3A%20our%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecf50696-d41c-44af-a191-d6e041165dae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'leaderboard'%20can%20gamify%20a%20wonky%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20and%20help%20it%20go%20viral%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENatalie%20Andreas%2C%20a%20communications%20studies%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20at%20Austin%20and%20digital%20strategy%20consultant%2C%20said%20Musk's%20leaderboard%20%26quot%3Bhas%20intriguing%20potential%20as%20a%20viral%2C%20high-impact%20marketing%20strategy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%2C%20like%20a%20social%20media%20feed%2C%20the%20format%20%26quot%3Bencourages%20frequent%20checking%20and%20sharing%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20public%20involvement%20through%20voting%20or%20sharing%20could%20fuel%20viral%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAyelet%20Fishbach%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20behavioral%20science%20and%20marketing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago's%20Booth%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20said%20a%20leaderboard%20takes%20advantage%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bgamification%26quot%3B%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20strategy%20can%20be%20entertaining%20%E2%80%94%20which%20helps%20a%20prospective%20audience%20stay%20engaged.%20And%20an%20engaged%20audience%20can%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20pass%20on%20information%20to%20their%20friends%20and%20other%20social%20media%20contacts%2C%20disseminating%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20as%20Musk%20himself%20said%20about%20the%20leaderboard%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20entertainment%20value%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1856524169338314838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepic%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22419ad8c4-6323-4c1e-bac7-7bc5394716b5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInteractivity%20helps%20give%20an%20audience%20a%20feeling%20of%20control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20promised%20a%20virtual%20suggestion%20box%20where%20the%20public%20can%20give%20him%20tips%20on%20what%20to%20cut%20or%20protect.%20%26quot%3BAnytime%20the%20public%20thinks%20we%20are%20cutting%20something%20important%20or%20not%20cutting%20something%20wasteful%2C%20just%20let%20us%20know!%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Musk%20and%20Trump's%20representatives%20didn't%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20in%20a%20dry%20realm%20like%20government%20spending%2C%20Musk's%20plans%20are%20bound%20to%20grab%20eyeballs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20make%20people%20feel%20more%20invested%20in%20the%20outcome.%20And%20in%20an%20environment%20with%20so%20many%20distractions%20%E2%80%94%20social%20media%2C%20streaming%20video%2C%20text%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20attention%20is%20a%20valuable%20commodity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreas%20said%20the%20leaderboard%20could%20strengthen%20Musk's%20brand%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20bold%2C%20transparency-driven%20disruptor%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20she%20also%20cautioned%20that%20it%20also%20would%20need%20%26quot%3Bcareful%20handling%26quot%3B%20to%20let%20the%20people%20and%20organizations%20targeted%20by%20the%20board%20add%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20allowing%20users%20to%20vote%20or%20contribute%20examples%20of%20perceived%20waste%20%26quot%3Bcould%20drive%20high%20engagement%20and%20user-generated%20content%2C%20making%20the%20leaderboard%20both%20interactive%20and%20addictive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20North%2C%20a%20clinical%20professor%20of%20communication%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California's%20Annenberg%20School%20for%20Communication%20and%20Journalism%2C%20said%20the%20venture%20also%20speaks%20to%20Trump's%20unique%20ability%20to%20spark%20an%20emotional%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20encourage%20vilification%20%E2%80%94%20in%20American%20politics.%20North%20previously%20served%20in%20the%20Clinton%20administration's%20science%20and%20technology%20policy%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20leaderboard%20marks%20another%20example%20of%20how%20the%20president-elect%20turns%20politics%20%26quot%3Binto%20a%20show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20more%20boring%20than%20talking%20about%20reducing%20spending%20in%20government.%20It's%20worse%20than%20just%20doing%20math%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20math%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290bc8724-304c-43f5-b31a-17725260dea9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20risks%20to%20the%20gamification%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20said%20the%20gamification%20strategy%20comes%20with%20risks.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20be%20so%20easily%20drawn%20into%20playing%20'gotcha'%20and%20being%20outraged%20that%20they%20may%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20outcome%20rather%20than%20the%20meaningful%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20gamifying%20the%20subject%20makes%20it%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20and%20social%20media%20has%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bparticipatory%20society%26quot%3B%20where%20people%20feel%20even%20more%20involved%20and%20invested%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20some%20precedent%20for%20Musk's%20leaderboard%2C%20North%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20former%20Sen.%20William%20Proxmire%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Wisconsin%2C%20began%20to%20issue%20the%20%26quot%3BGolden%20Fleece%20Award%26quot%3B%20for%20wasteful%20spending%20throughout%20the%201970s%20and%20'80s%20via%20monthly%20press%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20said%20it%20is%20often%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20PR%20campaigns%20in%20government%20history%2C%20though%20she%20cautioned%20that%20it%20did%20lead%20to%20some%20unforeseen%20consequences%3A%20Some%20research%20that%20was%20initially%20ridiculed%20as%20wasteful%20government%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldengooseaward.org%2F01awardees%2Fscrewworms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esexual%20behavior%20of%20screwworms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20later%20proved%20critical%20to%20the%20US%20livestock%20industry%20and%20significantly%20reduced%20beef%20costs%20for%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Amy%20Jo%20Kim%2C%20a%20game%20designer%20who%20has%20a%20doctoral%20degree%20in%20behavioral%20neuroscience%20and%20who's%20taught%20game%20design%20at%20Stanford%2C%20said%20that%20a%20leaderboard%20can%20inherently%20contain%20a%20point%20of%20view%3A%20Who's%20to%20determine%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20what's%20%26quot%3Bwaste%26quot%3B%20and%20how%20that's%20defined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Ba%20storytelling%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20opposite%20of%20transparency%2C%20but%20it'll%20be%20seen%20as%20transparency%20by%20people%20that%20don't%20realize%20that%20it%20all%20comes%20back%20to%20who%20defines%20waste.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-leaderboard-government-spending-marketing-genius-doge-donald-trump-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731535834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.