e%20US%20in%202023%2C%20Mr%20Rubio%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20is%20crucial%20that%20the%20Biden%20Administration%2C%20and%20the%20US%20Congress%2C%20prioritise%20this%20incredibly%20important%20relationship.%20Our%20nations'%20economic%20and%20security%20interests%20overlap%20on%20many%20of%20the%20most%20pressing%20issues%2C%20especially%20the%20growing%20hostility%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20and%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20potential%20status%20would%20solidify%20India-US%20tech%20and%20military%20ties.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20bill%20seeks%20to%20bar%20Pakistan%20from%20receiving%20security%20assistance%20if%20found%20sponsoring%20terrorism%20against%20India.%20Mr%20Rubio%20has%20historically%20been%20critical%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20urging%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Rex%20Tillerson%20to%20designate%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20of%20particular%20concern%26quot%3B%20for%20religious%20freedom%20violations%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Trump's%20victory%20and%20Marco%20Rubio's%20nomination%20bring%20optimism%20for%20India-US%20relations%2C%20promising%20a%20stronger%2C%20more%20strategic%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMIKE%20WALTZ%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump's%20appointment%20of%20Mike%20Waltz%20as%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20is%20expected%20to%20strengthen%20US-India%20ties%2C%20particularly%20in%20defence.%20Mr%20Waltz%2C%20a%20vocal%20China%20critic%20and%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Congressional%20India%20Caucus%2C%20has%20long%20advocated%20for%20deeper%20cooperation%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20to%20counter%20China's%20growing%20influence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20leadership%20may%20lead%20to%20expanded%20military%20cooperation%2C%20joint%20exercises%2C%20and%20enhanced%20sharing%20of%20defence%20technologies%2C%20aligning%20US%20and%20Indian%20strate