0Murmu%20praised%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20capabilities%20and%20strategic%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Navy%20units%20are%20deployed%20across%20vast%20areas%20for%20extended%20durations%2C%20showcasing%20their%20capabilities%20and%20strategic%20influence.%20Your%20positive%2C%20proactive%2C%20and%20swift%20actions%20have%20saved%20countless%20lives%20at%20sea.%20It%20was%20a%20special%20moment%20for%20me%20when%20the%20President%20of%20Bulgaria%20called%20to%20express%20gratitude%20for%20rescuing%20the%20Bulgarian%20crew%20from%20a%20hijacked%20vessel%20earlier%20this%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731523680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdi1141k8_commander-prerna-deosthalee-_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-sibling-duo-commands-warships-in-indian-navy-for-the-first-time-7013340%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20in%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20sister%20and%20brother%20duo%20of%20Commander%20Prerna%20Deosthalee%20and%20Commander%20Ishan%20Deosthalee%20are%20commanding%20two%20different%20warships%20at%20the%20same%20time%20in%20the%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Rally%20Stage%2C%20A%20Owaisi%20Served%20Notice%20To%20Avoid%20Inflammatory%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20has%20been%20served%20notice%20by%20the%20police%20in%20poll-bound%20Maharashtra's%20Solapur%20over%20his%20speeches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20was%20served%20to%20Mr%20Owaisi%20while%20he%20was%20on%20a%20crowded%20stage%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Solapur%20assembly