wo%20children%20-%20who%20went%20missing%20along%20with%20their%20mother%20and%20three%20others%20from%20Manipur's%20Jiribam%20after%20an%20encounter%20between%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20-%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20authorities%20to%20find%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20women%20from%20the%20family%2C%20and%20an%20eight-year-old%20child%20are%20also%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20were%20shot%20dead%20in%20Jiribam%20on%20Monday.%20Kuki%20groups%20have%20alleged%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20who%20were%20shot%20from%20behind%20by%20the%20CRPF%20without%20any%20provocation%2C%20an%20allegation%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaisharam%20Herojit%2C%20a%20low-level%20worker%20in%20the%20state%20government%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20appealed%20to%20any%20group%20that%20may%20have%20held%20his%20family%20hostage.%20He%20told%20NDTV%20that%20a%20friend%20of%20his%20wife%20saw%20them%20being%20taken%20away%20on%20a%20boat%20by%20armed%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20Laishram%20Herojit.%20I'm%20a%20resident%20of%20Thambalkhong.%20I'm%20a%20low-level%20government%20servant.%20Among%20the%20six%20missing%20people%2C%20my%20wife%2C%20my%20two%20children%2C%20my%20mother-in-law%20and%20wife's%20sister%20are%20there.%20So%20far%20there%20is%20no%20information%20about%20any%20of%20them.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20whether%20they%20are%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Herojit%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20all%20innocent.%20My%20two%20children%20cannot%20even%20speak%20yet.%20The%20elder%20one%20has%20just%20about%20started%20to%20speak.%20Please%20release%20them%20unhurt%20and%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Herojit%20told%20NDTV%20he%20got%20a%20call%20from%20his%20wife%20when%20shooting%20and%20arson%20broke%20out%20in%20Jiribam's%20Borobekra%20on%20Monday.%20The%20call%20got%20disconnected%20and%20when%20he%20dialled%20her%20back%2C%20he%20found%20the%20phone%20was%20switched%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20crying%20on%20the%20phone.%20She%20said%20they%20were%20surrounded%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20armed%20people.%20The%20call%20got%20disconnected%2C%20after%20which%20I%20called%20her%20back%2C%20but%20the%20mobile%20was%20switched%20off.%20My%20mother-in-law's%20phone%20was%20also%20switched%20off.%20About%20an%20hour%20later%20-%20and%20we%20had%20been%20searching%20for%20a%20while%20-%20a%20Bengali%20friend%20of%20my%20wife%20told%20us%20she%20saw%20them%20being%20taken%20away%20in%20a%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Herojit%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ftngb90fg_jiribam_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20camp%20and%20the%20police%20station%20in%20Jiribam's%20Borobekra%20are%20less%20than%201%20km%20from%20the%20Barak%20River%20(see%20map%20above).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yellow%20line%20is%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20river%20and%20the%20CRPF%20camp%20(approximately%20600%20metres)%2C%20while%20the%20white%20line%20is%20the%20distance%20between%20a%20small%20settlement%20and%20the%20police%20station%20(approximately%20350%20metres).%20The%20small%20settlement%20is%20on%20the%20upper%20tip%20of%20the%20white%20arrow.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20houses%20were%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20the%20suspected%20Kuki%20insurgents%20after%20attacking%20the%20police%20station%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRPF%20engaged%20them%20in%20the%20open%20stretch%20between%20the%20larger%20settlement%20towards%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20river%20and%20the%20camp%2C%20which%20is%20next%20to%20the%20small%20settlement%20that%20was%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20an%20extremely%20chaotic%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeitei%20Community%20Holds%20Silent%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20held%20candlelight%20vigil%20and%20protests%20in%20some%20cities%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20situation%20back%20home.%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20called%20a%20shutdown%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20and%20other%20valley%20areas%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20attack%20by%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20in%20Jiribam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fhk5cfjfg_meitei-protest_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeitei%20Alliance%2C%20a%20global%20umbrella%20body%20of%20civil%20groups%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bhostage-taking%20of%20three%20children%20and%20three%20women%20by%20Kuki%20terrorist%20groups...%20is%20an%20atrocity%20that%20demands%20immediate%20action.%20These%20terrorist%20groups%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20narrow%20ethnocentric%20agenda%2C%20must%20be%20rooted%20out%20at%20all%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20time%20for%20restraint%20is%20over.%20This%20is%20a%20make-or-break%20moment%20for%20Manipur.%20We%20demand%20proactive%20measures%2C%20and%20we%20urge%20all%20elected%20leaders%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20affiliation%2C%20to%20fulfil%20their%20duty%20and%20help%20in%20bringing%20an%20end%20to%20this%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Meitei%20Alliance%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKuki%20Groups%20Question%20%26quot%3BEncounter%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20student%20organisations%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20condemned%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3Bbarbaric%20actions%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF).%20They%20alleged%20the%2010%20men%20were%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Btreacherously%20murdered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaolienlal%20Haokip%2C%20one%20of%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20who%20have%20been%20seeking%20a%20separate%20administration%20citing%20alleged%20atrocities%20and%20unfair%20treatment%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20questioned%20the%20decision%20to%20send%20more%20central%20forces%20to%20Manipur%20after%20the%20Jiribam%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fcp6b9t0o_kuki-protest_625x300_12_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20rushing%20more%20CAPF%20(Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces)%20the%20solution%3F%20While%20totally%20neglecting%20the%20political%20process%3F%26quot%3B%20Manipur%20BJP%20MLA%20Mr%20Haokip%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20you%20refuse%20to%20recognise%20the%20political%20problem%2C%20continue%20to%20back%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20ethnic%20purge%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20rushing%20in%20more%20forces%20will%20only%20result%20in%20more%20deaths.%20Volunteers%20defending%20their%20villages%20are%20dubbed%20suspected%20militants%2C%20and%20a%20political%20problem%20is%20being%20handled%20as%20a%20law%20and%20order%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Haokip%2C%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Delegation%20Meets%20Assam%20Governor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Congress%20delegation%20in%20Assam%20met%20the%20Governor%20to%20express%20concern%20over%20the%20growing%20crisis%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%2C%20particularly%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20the%20six%20people.%20Former%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh%20said%20the%20situation%20continues%20to%20deteriorate%20with%20each%20passing%20day%2C%20made%20an%20urgent%20appeal%20for%20the%20Governor's%20intervention%2C%20and%20called%20for%20the%20Centre's%20active%20role%20in%20ensuring%20their%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJiribam%20is%20right%20on%20the%20interstate%20border%20with%20Assam.%20Sources%20said%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Congress%20delegation%20meeting%20the%20Assam%20Governor%20may%20be%20due%20to%20the%20suspicion%20that%20militants%20could%20be%20crossing%20between%20Assam%20and%20Manipur%20using%20Barak%20River%20in%20the%20Borobekra%20stretch.%20Sources%20said%20this%20reinforces%20the%20claim%20by%20Mr%20Herojit%20that%20his%20family%20was%20taken%20away%20in%20a%20boat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fqoa3a908_manipur-congress_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELatest%20Round%20Of%20Violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20round%20of%20violence%20in%20Jiribam%20began%20on%20Thursday%20last%20when%20suspected%20Meitei%20insurgents%20attacked%20a%20village%20of%20the%20Hmar%20tribe.%20A%20woman%20from%20the%20Hmar%20tribe%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20Her%20husband%20in%20a%20police%20case%20alleged%20she%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%2C%20raped%20and%20then%20set%20on%20fire%20by%20the%20suspected%20Meitei%20militants.%20Civil%20society%20groups%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20accused%20the%20Manipur%20government%20of%20keeping%20silent%20on%20Thursday's%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20was%20shot%20dead%20allegedly%20by%20suspected%20Kuki%20militants%20while%20working%20in%20a%20paddy%20field%20in%20the%20valley%20district%20Bishnupur.%20While%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20groups%20alleged%20the%20firing%20came%20from%20a%20nearby%20hill%2C%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20denied%20the%20shooting%2C%20citing%20the%20long%20distance%20from%20the%20nearest%20hill%20to%20the%20paddy%20field%20where%20the%20woman%20was%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley.%20The%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20-%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20-%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731519960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpjmjm3i8_laisharam-herojit_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-child-cant-speak-yet-manipur-man-appeals-for-safe-release-of-family-missing-after-jiribam-encounter-7011485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20two%20children%20-%20who%20went%20missing%20along%20with%20their%20mother%20and%20three%20others%20from%