ltz%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Congressional%20India%20Caucus%2C%20said%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20America%20will%20%26quot%3Bdetermine%20whether%20this%20is%20a%20century%20of%20light%20or%20a%20century%20of%20darkness%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congressman%20made%20these%20remarks%20at%20an%20event%20hosted%20by%20the%20US-India%20Strategic%20and%20Partnership%20Forum%20(USISPF)%20at%20Stanford%20University%20for%20the%20INDUSUSX%20Summit%20in%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bottom%20line%20is%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20this%20(US-India)%20is%20the%20most%20important%20relationship%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%20This%20will%20determine%20whether%20this%20is%20a%20century%20of%20light%20or%20a%20century%20of%20darkness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Waltz%20said%20in%20his%20video%20message%20to%20the%20summit%2C%20which%20he%20could%20not%20attend%20due%20to%20his%20engagements%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20encouraged%20further%20collaboration%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20maintain%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20protect%20India's%20sovereignty%2C%20particularly%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsider%20my%20office%20and%20my%20team%20an%20open%20door%20to%20further%20this%20relationship%20as%20we%20press%20forward%2C%20and%20keeping%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20free%20and%20open%20and%20protecting%20Indian%20sovereignty%20particularly%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20world%20that%20we%20leave%20behind%20for%20our%20children%20and%20grandchildren%20is%20in%20line%20with%20our%20shared%20values%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Waltz%20further%20emphasised%20that%20he%20was%20excited%20about%20the%20enormous%20momentum%20in%20the%20partnership%20between%20the%20oldest%20and%20the%20largest%20democracies%20in%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20keep%20the%20momentum%20(in%20the%20US-India%20relationship)%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20growing%20momentum%20in%20US-India%20relations%20is%20evident%20through%20initiatives%20like%20iCET%20and%20INDUS-X%2C%20and%20highlighted%20several%20areas%20of%20cooperation%20including%20joint%20production%20of%20the%20Apache%20helicopter%20fuselages%20by%20Boeing%20and%20Tata%2C%20advancements%20in%20ship%20repair%2C%20quantum%20computing%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20data%20management%20-%20all%20of%20which%20are%20crucial%20for%20both%20nations%20to%20advance%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Waltz%20visited%20India%20in%20August%20with%20his%20co-chair%20Congressman%20Ro%20Khanna%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Congressman%20also%20praised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%E2%80%9D%20address%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%2C%20and%20called%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%20%26quot%3Ban%20amazing%20event.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731510660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frk0ie17s_narendra-modi-donald-trump-modi-trump-afp_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-donald-trumps-nsa-nominee-mike-waltz-said-on-indias-pivotal-role-in-the-21st-century-7010548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mike%20Waltz%2C%20named%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20by%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20emphasised%20that%20he%20was%20excited%20about%20the%20enormous%20momentum%20in%20the%20partnership%20between%20US%20and%20India%20-%20the%20oldest%20and%20the%20largest%20democracies%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-donald-trumps-nsa-nominee-mike-waltz-said-on-indias-pivotal-role-in-the-21st-century-7010548%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22