ashtra%2C%20Shah%20stepped%20up%20his%20campaigning%20for%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20front%2C%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20member%2C%20and%20addressed%20three%20rallies%20in%20a%20day%20where%20he%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20ally%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Dhule%20in%20North%20Maharashtra%2C%20Shah%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20remember%20that%20even%20if%20his%20%26quot%3Bfourth%20generation%20was%20to%20come%26quot%3B%2C%20Muslims%20won't%20get%20reservations%20meant%20for%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%20and%20other%20backward%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Ulemas%20(Muslim%20scholars)%20met%20the%20president%20of%20Congress%20party%20and%20said%20Muslims%20should%20be%20given%20reservation%20(in%20jobs%20and%20education).%20If%20reservation%20has%20to%20be%20given%20to%20Muslims%2C%20then%20reservations%20for%20SCs%2FSTs%2FOBCs%20will%20have%20to%20be%20cut.%20Rahul%20Baba%2C%20not%20only%20you%20but%20even%20if%20your%20four%20generations%20were%20to%20come%2C%20they%20cannot%20cut%20the%20quota%20meant%20for%20SCs%2FSTs%2FOBCs%20and%20give%20it%20to%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Article%20370%2C%20scrapped%20in%202019%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%2C%20won't%20be%20restored%20under%20any%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20Indira%20Gandhi%20were%20to%20return%20from%20heaven%2C%20Article%20370%20won't%20be%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20stalwart%20told%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20opposition%20MVA%20grouping%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BAurangzeb%20Fan%20Club%26quot%3B%2C%20Shah%20noted%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20abides%20by%20the%20ideals%20of%20Maratha%20warrior%20king%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20and%20freedom%20fighter%20Veer%20Savarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20election%20meeting%20in%20Jalgaon%2C%20also%20in%20North%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20former%20BJP%20president%20averred%20that%20if%20the%20MVA%20wins%20the%20November%2020%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20state%20will%20turn%20into%20an%20ATM%20(automated%20teller%20machine)%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(MVA)%20will%20withdraw%20funds%20from%20Maharashtra%20by%20using%20the%20state's%20resources%20and%20send%20the%20money%20to%20Delhi.%20In%20contrast%2C%20if%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20forms%20a%20government%2C%20the%20Modi%20administration%20will%20ensure%20greater%20development%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said%20at%20the%20meeting%20in%20Chalisgaon%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20he%20accused%20his%20party%20of%20making%20false%20promises%20and%20misleading%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20seen%20waving%20a%20copy%20of%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar's%20Constitution.%20He%20used%20the%20same%20copy%20while%20taking%20the%20oath%20in%20Parliament.%20When%20some%20journalists%20got%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20very%20copy%2C%20it%20had%20blank%20pages.%20By%20showing%20a%20fake%20Constitution%2C%20Rahul%20broke%20the%20trust%20of%20people%20and%20insulted%20Babasaheb.%20Apparently%2C%20you%20have%20never%20read%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Rahul%20baba%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BSonia-Manmohan%20regime%26quot%3B%20didn't%20act%20against%20Naxalism%20and%20terrorism%20for%2010%20years%20(2004-14)%20due%20to%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Congress%20politics%20runs%20on%20deception.%20They%20are%20saying%20that%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20(in%20June%202022)%2C%20investment%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20reduced.%20The%20truth%20is%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government%20of%20(CM)%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20(deputy%20CM)%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20our%20Maharashtra%20is%20No.1%20state%20in%20FDI%20inflows%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Mahayuti%20government%20post-polls%20will%20work%20more%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20women%2C%20farmers%20and%20other%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20Shah%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20one%20vote%20will%20not%20only%20form%20a%20Mahayuti%20government%20but%20your%20one%20vote%20will%20also%20deposit%20Rs%202%2C100%20in%20the%20account%20of%20Maharashtra's%20beloved%20sisters.%20Your%20one%20vote%20will%20result%20in%20depositing%20Rs%2015%2C000%20instead%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20annually%20in%20farmers'%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20guarantee%20is%20like%20'patthar%20ki%20lakeer'%20(carved%20in%20stone)%2C%20whereas%20the%20Congress%20reneged%20on%20pre-poll%20promises%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20NCP%20(SP)%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Shah%20said%20the%20senior%20politician%20served%20as%20Maharashtra%20CM%20and%20also%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20for%20many%20years%2C%20but%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20to%20give%20classical%20language%20status%20to%20Marathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20third%20rally%20at%20Jintur%20in%20Parbhani%20district%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region%2C%20Shah%20averred%20that%20Congress%20MP%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20campaigning%20for%20the%20MVA%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20will%20fail%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSonia%20ji%20tried%20to%20land%20the%20plane%20named%20Rahul%20Baba%2020%20times%20and%2020%20times%20the%20plane%20crashed.%20Now%20again%2C%20an%20attempt%20is%20being%20made%20to%20land%20the%20plane%20for%20the%2021st%20time%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Sonia