radesh%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2084%20on%20Day%201%20by%20Goa.%20He%20returned%20figures%20of%205%2F25%2C%20dismissing%20Neelam%20Obi%2C%20Nabam%20Hachang%2C%20Chinmay%20Patil%2C%20Jay%20Bhavsar%20and%20Moji%20Ete.%20The%2025-year-old%20was%20ably%20supported%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohit%20Redkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F120061-mohit-redkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohit%20Redkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(3%2F15)%20and%20Keith%20Pinto%20(2%2F31)%20as%20Arunachal%20Pradesh's%20innings%20folded%20in%2030.3%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETendulkar%20got%20the%20ball%20rolling%20with%20the%20wicket%20of%20Hachang%20(0)%20in%20the%20second%20over%20of%20the%20match.%20He%20was%20on%20a%20hattrick%20after%20dismissing%20Obi%20and%20Bhavsar%20off%20consecutive%20deliveries%20in%20the%2012th%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatil%20and%20Ete%20were%20his%20final%20two%20scalps%20before%20Redkar%20and%20Pinto%20joined%20the%20party%20and%20cleaned%20Arunachal's%20tail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun's%20exploits%20comes%20after%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20decided%20not%20to%20retain%20him%20for%20IPL%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20likelyhood%2C%20Arjun%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20warmed%20up%20for%20the%20undergoing%20first-class%20season%20with%20a%20match-winning%20nine-wicket%20haul%20in%20Goa's%20innings%20and%20189-run%20victory%20over%20hosts%20Karnataka%20in%20the%20Dr%20(Capt)%20K%20Thimmappiah%20Memorial%20Tournament%2C%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20KSCA%20Invitational%2C%20a%20pre-season%20meet%20for%20state%20teams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSCA%20XI%20comprised%20mostly%20their%20U-19%20and%20U-23%20players%20with%20only%20two%20established%20names%20--%20Nikin%20Jose%20and%20glovesman%20Sharath%20Srinivas%20--%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legendary%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20son%20had%20a%20match%20haul%20of%209%20for%2087%20in%2026.3%20overs%20across%20two%20innings.%20In%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20Karnataka%20folded%20for%20103%20in%2036.5%20overs%20with%20Tendulkar%20junior%20taking%205%2F41%20in%2013%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20Goa%20posted%20a%20solid%20413%20as%20Abhinav%20Tejrana%20(109)%20scored%20a%20hundred%20and%20Manthan%20Khutkar%20contributed%2069.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20KSCA%20XI%20were%20a%20shade%20better%2C%20being%20shot%20out%20for%20121%20in%2030.4%20overs%20with%20Arjun%20grabbing%204%20for%2046%20in%2013.3%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731492060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fc2830gmg_arjun-tendulkar-ranji-trophy_625x300_13_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Franji-trophy%2Freleased-by-mumbai-indians-arjun-tendulkar-sends-loud-message-with-maiden-ranji-trophy-5-wicket-haul-7009087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20his%20release%20by%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Arjun%20Tendulkar%20picked%20his%20maiden%20five-wicket%20haul%20in%20First%20Class%20cricket%20as%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2084%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maps%20and%20data%20reveal%20how%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%20have%20reached%20record%20levels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731491580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F11%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-dandf-teaser-drones_6747343.png%3F20241113121657%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdrone-attacks-on-ukraine-reach-record-levels-as-russia-could-be-stockpiling-missiles-for-winter-assault-13253518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20dramatically%20scaled%20up%20its%20long-range%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20that%20analysts%20say%20cou