ge.%20However%2C%20Bhati%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20begun%20to%20shift%20that%20perception%2C%20even%20if%20just%20a%20little.%20For%20example%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20with%20Ganga%20and%20Sundar%2C%20a%20mother-daughter%20duo.%20To%20see%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20once%20lacked%20confidence%20and%20had%20never%20sung%20outside%20her%20home%20now%20performing%20at%20shows%20and%20private%20events%20is%20the%20biggest%20reward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20speaking%20with%20Ganga%2C%20who%20is%20as%20sweet%20in%20conversation%20as%20she%20is%20bold%20in%20song%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20family%20of%20musicians%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20singing%20from%20my%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20could%20reach%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20reassuring%20to%20see%20young%20women%20participate%20in%20our%20residency%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20their%20parents%20trust%20us%20enough%20to%20let%20them%20attend%20without%20accompaniment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%20This%20trust%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strong%20relationships%20they%E2%80%99ve%20built%20within%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20the%20music%20alive%3A%20Supporting%20artists%20through%20the%20pandemic%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20folk%20artists%2C%20their%20livelihood%20depends%20entirely%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20perform%2C%20but%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%2C%20when%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20stage%2C%20the%20impact%20was%20devastating%20for%20entire%20communities.%20To%20support%20them%2C%20Sharon%20facilitated%20a%20collaboration%20with%20My%20Mensa%2C%20a%20visual%20learning%20app%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300577%2Fbest-folk-artists-and-artisans-take-masterclasses-on-first-culture-tech-platform-memeraki%2F%5C%22%20targ