class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(Northeast%20Waste%20Collective)%20have%20been%20doing%20good%20work%3B%20and%20the%20best%20part%20about%20them%20being%20here%20is%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20it%20considering%20the%20local%20sentiments%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Akriti%20Sagar%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20cum%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20West%20Kameng.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20all%20good%20stories%2C%20the%20Northeast%20Waste%20Collective%E2%80%99s%20journey%20was%20fraught%20with%20challenges%20and%20lessons%20from%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20student%20to%20sustainability%20champion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIttisha%E2%80%99s%20journey%20as%20a%20waste%20warrior%20began%20after%20she%20completed%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20economics%20from%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Symbiosis%20Institute%20of%20Technology.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20my%20cup%20of%20tea.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20myself%20working%20in%20a%20corporate%20setting.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%20but%20I%20did%20know%20what%20%E2%80%98not%E2%80%99%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20course%20on%20social%20design%20offered%20by%20Ambedkar%20University%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was%20then.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20time%20hearing%20the%20term%2C%20but%20the%20design%20aspect%20intrigued%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20combination%20of%20%E2%80%98social%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98design%E2%80%99%20piqued%20my%20curiosity%2C%20so%20I%20applied%20for%20the%20course.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20step%20outside%20the%20c