%20guidance%2C%20how%20can%20detainees%20be%20expected%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20lives%20once%20they%20leave%20jail%3F%20The%20quest%20for%20answers%20led%20Dr%20Bedi%20to%20design%20a%20model%20that%20would%20hand-hold%20convicts%2C%20not%20just%20during%20their%20sentence%20but%20also%20post-acquittal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20model%20targeted%20at%20supporting%20inmates%20and%20their%20families%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20computers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20boasts.%20He%20then%20lists%20a%20series%20of%20tech-related%20odd%20jobs%20that%20he%20held%20prior%20to%20his%20conviction%2C%20though%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20pursued%20a%20formal%20degree.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20used%20my%20time%20in%20jail%20to%20complete%20a%20computer%20course%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20will%20help%20me%20get%20a%20good%20job.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20also%20used%20his%20time%20in%20prison%20to%20hone%20his%20artistic%20skills.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20free%20man%20after%20being%20declared%20innocent%20by%20the%20court%20in%20July%202024%2C%20he%20is%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F92425%2Findian-businessman-prisoners-jailed-petty-aid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20believes%20will%20open%20up%20in%20the%20job%20market.%20Akshay%20credits%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Inside%20Prison%20Program%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20which%20impacted%20over%202%2C68%2C853%20inmates%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20for%20giving%20him%20this%20new%20lease%20on%20life.%20He%20says%20that%20it%20helped%20him%20preserve%20his%20sanity%20while%20in%20prison.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3